{"tid":1472543,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[幫推] 警世!! 每個人之間一定要有 一隻手距離!! 保人自保!!","createTime":"2019-08-14T15:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T05:47:52.000Z","uid":67372,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"68e9674ba01b53c6cb3b62005ac34ac01962d17b","tid":1472543,"uid":67372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:07:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">雖然勇武休息緊 但所有上得街嘅人都要知 咁就係對勇武最好嘅支援</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 保留空間 間距</span><br />\n就好似你睇文章咁，唔隔行無標點實睇撚死人，同樣，每個人無<span style=\"color: red;\">一隻手距離</span>嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\">a)視野會被擋只能等人大叫去接收消息而唔係由自身作出即時反應，b)空間不流通，揸水筒嘅手足會好難搵二手煙源頭<br />\n</span><br />\n導致: 中後排手足反應唔切，頂住前排向後跑繼而落單 : 唔夠快滅煙D狗好容易係濃煙掩護下衝出黎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 防臥底狗 鬼</span><br />\n深水埗有試過D鬼係防暴衝時拉住手足個袋去令佢跑唔走，就係因為人同人之間無一隻手距離，<span style=\"color: red;\">企得太埋小左戒心</span>。銅鑼灣個單，如果大家有適當距離時，會<span style=\"color: red;\">多左幾秒掙扎同大叫支援既緩衝</span>，而唔係即刻俾人㩒低<br />\n<br />\n對策: 觀察力強嘅手足可以利用呢個一隻手距離去留意你覺得嘅鬼，鬼附近實有照應，慢慢搵出共通點然後就同現場真手足決定行動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">3. 去群體化 真be water</span><br />\n當人同人有一隻手距離，<span style=\"color: red;\">散嘅時候一定順暢好多</span>，而係狗嘅角度就會追唔切嬲豬，谷到行導致出錯，例子有 新城市狗單拖應聲彈出，衝上電梯俾手足輪 : 深水埗狗跑極唔停，俾白衫狗敲盾<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一隻手距離 唔撚洗人提</span></div></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個係一個<span style=\"color: red;\">安全距離 </span>係對一個行動群體嘅基本條件 同時唔會阻到人 又保護到自己<br />\n<br />\n幾時要用？隨時，就好似你行街搭巴士都唔會膊頭掂膊頭，所以記住 間距 距離<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Be Water</div>"},{"pid":"f3bbc0d76ecb39e90cb104b977fdbba02652c29d","tid":1472543,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ly5Jp5H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLy5Jp5H.jpg&h=d3697d4a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hBCzwLH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhBCzwLH.jpg&h=bad0d9fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32072e253794514ee54050578fea35ff1d104998","tid":1472543,"uid":67372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:22:11.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"c5c7d3d55b9771d671b07bd32d12270a2b7984ca","tid":1472543,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:32:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n長期戰 不氣餒</span></ins></em></strong></span><br />\n唔好意思，阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n香港人重要日程：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>8月15日</strong>：稅局接收工（1200稅務大樓）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月16日</strong>：學界萬人炒聯手萬人集會（2000遮打花園）<br />\n<strong>8月16日</strong>：大家記得撳錢</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>8月17日</strong>：教師大遊行（1100遮打花園）<br />\n<strong>8月17日</strong>：光復紅土（1530紅磡馬頭）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月18日</strong>：民陣大遊行（1500維園）</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月24日</strong>：觀塘大遊行（1300駿業街球場）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>8月25日</strong>：荃葵青遊街（1400葵青劇院集合）</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">各位手足，到時見！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"937fb63192e38b7cf6c4945d9333acf9f0acff71","tid":1472543,"uid":67372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:43:35.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"1320e27069dbdcf31066c64fd31a2f1f56283d4f","tid":1472543,"uid":200186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:44:07.000Z","msg":"我讀政政，入嚟教大家點樣提升政治運動成效<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470899</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 